value:
Programmes carried out by the Company includes the following topics and areas:
1. Internal Control Systems;
2. CSR strategy framework;
3. Industry evolution and competition insights;
4. Business Updates, New Business
5. Strategies, Business Models, Industry Outlook, Sharing updates about Competitive environment;
6. Update on LODR Amendments;
7. Legal and Regulatory Updates
8. Updates on Prevention of Insider Trading Regulations
9. Investor Grievances;
10. Risks and opportunities for the businesses including Risk Management and Risk Matrix;
11. Future outlook and the way forward;
12. Quarterly Updates on Business operations
13. Strategy Update by various functions
14. Internal Audit Plans and findings;
15. Compliances with various applicable laws;

